Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙翼蛇杖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡可以瞄準嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點遠  但我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用全部的力量把它幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現吧  出現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來  我最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖銀啊  爆裂吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個伊莉絲居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人  各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖銀啊  爆裂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂吧  爆裂吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請瞄準斥力場的裂痕進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貫穿吧  閃光！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實擊中了
