Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風彈四重奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,323)\fs18}Mjolnir
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷霆戰錘
